%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efirst%20year%20of%20university%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20previous%20spring%2C%20I%20had%20thought%20about%20which%20undergraduate%20degree%20I%20wanted%20to%20pursue%20for%20months%2C%20reading%20about%20courses%2C%20tuition%2C%20and%20life%20in%20a%20new%20place.%20Since%20I%20loved%20writing%20and%20dreamed%20of%20becoming%20a%20journalist%2C%20studying%20communication%20seemed%20like%20the%20best%20bet.%20I%20chose%20to%20pursue%20a%20degree%20at%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-business-schools-in-the-world-2018-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprivate%20university%20in%20Milan%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20the%20classes%20seemed%20fascinating%20and%20useful%2C%20and%20the%20idea%20of%20living%20in%20Milan%20was%20thrilling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20I%20soon%20realized%20I%20had%20made%20the%20wrong%20choice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225393752b-cfa8-4353-b7bb-fa10904b7e10%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20first%20year%20of%20undergrad%20in%20Milan%20was%20challenging%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20majority%20of%20the%20courses%20I%20was%20taking%20were%20engaging%2C%20but%20we%20occasionally%20experienced%20last-minute%20schedule%20changes%20and%20disorganized%20lecturers%2C%20and%20that%20didn't%20sit%20right%20with%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20importantly%2C%20I%20began%20to%20feel%20guilty%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fstudent-loans%2Faverage-college-tuition%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20expenses%3C%2Fa%3E%20my%20parents%20were%20covering%20for%20me.%20They%20assured%20me%20they%20could%20afford%20it%20and%20that%20my%20education%20was%20worthwhile%20to%20them%3B%20nonetheless%2C%20the%20tuition%20and%20rent%20were%20expensive.%20And%2C%20if%20I%20wasn't%20loving%20it%2C%20should%20they%20be%20spending%20so%20much%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELiving%20in%20Milan%20was%20way%20more%20exciting%20in%20my%20dreams%20than%20it%20was%20