ain%20a%20new%20visa%20stamp%2C%20I'm%20not%20sure%20there's%20a%20clear%20path%20to%20return.%20This%20includes%20individuals%20on%20F-1%20student%20visas%20who%20traveled%20to%20visit%20family%20and%20were%20planning%20to%20re-enter%20the%20US.%20They%20will%20need%20that%20visa%20stamp%20from%20a%20consulate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEnsure%20your%20employment%20is%20still%20active%20and%20consider%20whether%20remote%20work%20is%20an%20option.%20If%20an%20employer%20decides%20they%20cannot%20keep%20someone%20on%20the%20books%2C%20even%20an%20appointment%20months%20from%20now%20will%20not%20help%20if%20there's%20no%20job%20waiting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20tough%20to%20know%20how%20things%20will%20unfold.%20What%20we're%20seeing%20is%20a%20confluence%20of%20policies%20coming%20in%20at%20the%20same%20time.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20Department%20of%20Homeland%20Security%20has%20just%20announced%20that%20it%20is%20replacing%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fh1b-visa-lottery-new-rules-salary-big-tech-students-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elottery%20system%20for%20H-1B%20work%20visas%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20randomly%20selects%20who%20receives%20a%20visa.%20The%20system%20is%20now%20set%20to%20prioritize%20higher-paid%2C%20higher-skilled%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2284fd6b39-f22d-4778-b3e6-c70ff3cc85b7%5C%22%3EKeeping%20social%20media%20accounts%20public%20is%20a%20good%20idea%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESocial%20media%20disclosure%20is%20being%20expanded%20from%20F-1%20visa%20holders%2C%20which%20began%20during%20the%20student%20visa%20crisis%2C%20to%20now%20include%20H-1B%20workers.%20These%20applicants%20are%20required%20to%20change%20all%20social%20media%20privacy%20settings%20to%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20could%20easily%20expand%20to%20other%20visa%20categories.%20The%20government%20has%20not%20provided%20clear%20guidance%20on%20what%20they%20are%20reviewing.%20By%20casting%20an%20overly%20broad%20net%20under%20the