th%C3%A9e%20Chalamet%20insisted%20on%20being%20spanked%20for%20real%20in%20a%20scene%20in%20%26quot%3BMarty%20Supreme.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EKevin%20O'Leary%20told%20Business%20Insider%20he%20used%20a%20real%20ping%20pong%20paddle%20in%20the%20scene.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EO'Leary%20said%20the%20take%20where%20he%20hit%20Chalamet%20the%20hardest%20was%20used%20in%20the%20movie.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20%26quot%3BMarty%20Supreme%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftimothee-chalamet-facts-2018-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETimoth%C3%A9e%20Chalamet%3C%2Fa%3E%20plays%20a%20ping%20pong%20hustler%20who%20will%20stop%20at%20nothing%20to%20get%20his%20way.%20On%20the%20set%20of%20the%20Josh%20Safdie%20film%2C%20the%20star%20was%20similarly%20determined%20to%20get%20the%20right%20shot%20%E2%80%94%20even%20if%20it%20meant%20withstanding%20some%20physical%20pain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENear%20the%20end%20of%20the%20movie%2C%20Chalamet's%20character%20Marty%20Mauser%20begs%20business%20tycoon%20Milton%20Rockwell%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkevin-oleary-shark-tank-daily-routine-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EKevin%20O'Leary%3C%2Fa%3E)%20to%20front%20the%20money%20for%20a%20table%20tennis%20rematch%20in%20Japan%20against%20his%20rival%20Koto%20Endo%20(real-life%20table%20tennis%20champion%20Koto%20Kawaguchi).%20After%20Mauser%20initially%20declined%20Rockwell's%20gracious%20offer%20earlier%20in%20the%20movie%2C%20the%20businessman%20won't%20let%20him%20off%20easy%20this%20time.%20Rockwell%20agrees%20to%20hold%20the%20match%20%E2%80%94%20but%20only%20if%20he%20can%20first%20cut%20Mauser%20down%20to%20size.%20How%3F%20By%20spanking%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMauser%20reluctantly%20agrees.%20He%20drops%20his%20pants%20and%20bends%20over%20a%20chair%20as%20Rockwell%2C%20surrounded%20by%20party%20guests%2C%20spanks%20Mauser's%20bare%20bottom%20with%20a%20ping%20pong%20paddle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EO'Leary%