3EFrom%20the%20time%20the%20last%20leaf%20turns%20brown%20and%20falls%20to%20the%20ground%20to%20the%20time%20the%20first%20flakes%20of%20snow%20land%2C%20I%20know%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnasa-making-new-clock-moon-ticks-faster-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eclock%20is%20ticking%20down%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20December%2024%20%E2%80%94%20Lori's%20birthday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223db5c99b-4301-4e62-80b9-031427df2e48%5C%22%3EShe%20lived%20with%20a%20brain%20tumor%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20year%20was%20the%20roughest.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20most%20recent%20memory%20of%20her%20birthday%20was%20her%2051st%2C%20only%20a%20few%20weeks%20after%20the%20doctors%20said%20there%20was%20nothing%20left%20to%20do%20but%20wait%20for%20the%20inevitable.%20But%20Lori%20ignored%20that.%20For%2023%20years%2C%20she%20lived%20with%20a%20malignant%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-thought-my-sons-benign-brain-tumor-was-harmless-i-was-wrong-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebrain%20tumor%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20was%20told%20this%20is%20it.%20And%20then%2C%20it%20wasn't.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20what%20would%20be%20her%20last%20birthday%2C%20I%20made%20her%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freference%2Frainbow-cake%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethree-layer%20cake%3C%2Fa%3E%20filled%20with%20strawberries%20and%20covered%20in%20a%20chocolate%20ganache%2C%20prepared%20pancakes%20(which%20was%20her%20favorite%20food%20group)%2C%20and%20gave%20her%20chocolate%20from%20her%20favorite%20shop%2C%20a%20cubic%20zirconium%20engagement%20ring%20because%20her%20actual%20engagement%20ring%20no%20longer%20fit%20on%20her%20fingers%2C%20and%20a%20needlepoint%20kit%20that%20she%20could%20use%20from%20her%20wheelchair.%20And%20when%20she%20went%20to%20sleep%2C%20I%20cried.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20the%20memory%20stuck%20in%20my%20head.%20This%20was%20the%20memory%20that%20haunted%20me.%20And%20every%20year%20since%20she%20died%2C%20I%20hope%20that%20on%20the%20anniversary%20of%20her%20birthday%2C%20the%20memory%20of%20any%20one%20of%20the%20other%2033%20birthdays%20I%20celebrated%20with%20Lori%20would%20somehow%20show%20their%20face%2C%20and%20bring%20a%20smile%20instead%20of%20tears.%20For%20three%20years%20I%20waited.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220d72aa16-159a-453d-975e-762fd95b05b1%5C%22%3EI%20read%20her%20diaries%20from%20time%20to%20time%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%2C%20last%20year%2C%20it%20finally%20happened.%20On%20what%20would%20have%20been%20her%2055th%20birthday%2C%20I%20was%20reading%20Lori's%20diaries%2C%20which%20I%20did%20from%20time%20to%20time%2C%20pretending%20I%20could%20still%20talk%20with%20her.%20I%20came%20across%20a%20passage%20she%20wrote%20about%20her%2035th%20birthday.%20I%20smiled.%20Lori%20had%20just%20recovered%20from%20yet%20another%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-had-brain-surgery-while-conscious-fixed-my-tremor-disorder-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebrain%20surgery%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20radiation%20and%20told%20her%20doctors%20that%2C%20come%20the%20first%20snowstorm%2C%20she%20would%20be%20skiing.%20It%20had%20been%2010%20years%20since%20we%20got%20married%2C%20and%20as%20a%20birthday%20present%2C%20I%20thought%20we%20would%20invite%20friends%20and%20family%20to%20the%20summit%20of%20our%20favorite%20ski%20resort%20so%20we%20could%20renew%20our%20wedding%20vows.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20memories%20started%20rushing%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221938cd80-fc4c-44ac-8511-4520dfc9ac6b%5C%22%3EI%20remember%20that%20day%20vividly%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20December%2024%2C%202005%2C%20at%206%20a.m.%2C%20and%20there%20were%20already%20a%20couple%20of%20inches%20of%20snow%20on%20the%20ground.%20The%20forecast%20was%20calling%20for%2012%20more.%20The%20house%20smelled%20like%20last%20night's%20fireplace.%20I%20looked%20at%20Lori%20sleeping%20next%20to%20me.%20She%20was%20wearing%20her%20snowman%20pajama%20bottoms%20and%20a%20top%20she%20affectionately%20called%20her%20%26quot%3BThug%20Muppet.%26quot%3B%20It's%20essentially%20a%20super-soft%2C%20fleece-lined%20hoodie%20with%20neon%20orange%20drawstrings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20hated%20to%20wake%20her%2C%20but%20if%20I%20didn't%20give%20Lori%20her%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fgifts%2Funique-gift-websites%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebirthday%20gifts%3C%2Fa%3E%20immediately%2C%20we%20wouldn't%20have%20time%20alone%20again%20until%20the%20next%20day.%20She%20had%20spent%20the%20day%20before%20her%20birthday%20wrapping%20her%20ski%20poles%20with%20plastic%20flowers.%20There%20were%20orchids%2C%20roses%2C%20lilies%2C%20and%20lace%20to%20hold%20it%20all%20together.%20She%20put%20Powerpuff%20Girls%20stickers%20on%20her%20skis%20and%20laid%20out%20a%20little%20black%20dress%20(her%20standard%20evening%20uniform)%20as%20her%20outfit%20for%20the%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20leaned%20over%20and%20gently%20kissed%20her%20on%20the%20forehead%2C%20telling%20her%20it%20was%20time%20to%20wake%20up.%20As%20usual%2C%20she%20asked%20for%20five%20more%20minutes%2C%20telling%20me%20it%20was%20still%20dark%20outside.%20I%20whispered%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20snowing.%26quot%3B%20Lori's%20eyes%20light%20up.%20%26quot%3BWill%20we%20have%20time%20to%20do%20a%20run%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-ski-resorts-in-northeast-us-east-coast-skiing-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eterrain%20park%3C%2Fa%3E%20before%20the%20ceremony%3F%20I%20have%20a%20new%20trick%20I%20want%20to%20try.%26quot%3B%20I%20ask%20if%20we%20can%20try%20to%20avoid%20her%20breaking%20something%20until%20after%20the%20ceremony%20is%20over.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20rolled%20out%20of%20bed%2C%20saw%20the%20pile%20of%20presents%20on%20the%20floor%2C%20and%20immediately%20started%20tearing%20the%20wrapping%20paper%20off.%20Leaving%20a%20trail%20of%20crumpled%20paper%20throughout%20the%20house%2C%20Lori%20starts%20telling%20me%20the%20trick%20she%20wants%20to%20do.%20She%20blurts%20out%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20better%20than%20the%20one%20yesterday!%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Couple%20posing%20in%20the%20snow%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F691cc40189026fbb4d0de237%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221134%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20day%20before%2C%20she%20had%20jumped%20off%20a%20%26quot%3Bsmall%26quot%3B%20set%20of%20rocks%20while%20skiing%20in%20the%20trees.%20Usually%2C%20she%20follows%20me%20in%20the%20trees%2C%20but%20she%20decided%20I%20was%20moving%20too%20slowly.%20She%20was%20about%2025%20yards%20ahead%20of%20me%20when%20I%20heard%20%26quot%3BWoo%20Hoo!%26quot%3B%20and%20then%20she%20disappeared.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20so%20focused%20on%20trying%20to%20figure%20out%20where%20she%20went%20that%20I%20barely%20had%20time%20to%20brace%20myself%20before%20I%2C%20too%2C%20was%20in%20the%20air.%20My%20arms%20swing%20wildly%20like%20I%20am%20jumping%20rope%20in%20midair%20and%20just%20praying%20I%20don't%20face%20plant%20when%20I%20land.%20I%20see%20her%20now.%20Giggling%2C%20covered%20from%20head%20to%20toe%20in%20snow.%20Her%20skis%20and%20poles%20are%20strewn%20all%20over%20the%20snow%20in%20multiple%20directions.%20She%20looks%20like%20a%20yeti.%20Her%20smile%20is%20intoxicating.%20I%20can't%20help%20but%20start%20laughing%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDid%20you%20see%20that%3F%20I%20was%20flying.%26quot%3B%20I%20lie%20and%20say%20it%20was%20amazing.%20I%20usually%20can't%20watch%20when%20she%20does%20these%20tricks.%20I%20keep%20thinking%20she%20is%20going%20to%20crash.%20The%20parade%20of%20horrors%20that%20awaits%20reads%20like%20a%20top%2010%20list%20for%20what%20happens%20when%20stupid%20human%20tricks%